<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>zu verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
                        und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir zu disen
                            <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht
                            <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣre
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> noch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, denn in masse als wir ewch nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>corp<ex>or</ex>is</expan> Christi.</ab>
